<br>
Tyl could only stare at the man before her now, attempting to take in all that was happening. All that was happening so fast. <br>
<br>
Evelynne was a little less reluctant to act. <br>
<br>
Her blades already drawn, she boldly moved past Tyl to confront the elven rogue. Tyl outstretched an arm, turning her around to face her. Evelynne cast a shocked gaze at Tyl. <br>
<br>
